<description>
    <short>
        <en>Allow SSO agains multiple external identity providers using SAML2.</en>
    </short>
    <long>
        <en>This plugin is a 'rewrite' of Derrick Smiths phpsaml plugin using the latest GLPI10+ best practices like Marketplace, PSR, composer, twig and much more. 
            Glpisaml allows you to configure multiple external SAML identity providers for SSO. If the external identity provider also implements MFA (like azure) 
            this plugin can also be used to implement (external) MFA as well.

            Help build a helpfull GLPI community at our discord at: https://discord.gg/35tkHxHg
        </en>
    </long>
</description>
